{"tid":1882183,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Taylor憑爛片《CATS》爭兒童奧斯卡影后","createTime":"2020-02-16T05:41:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T08:45:11.000Z","uid":41343,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8483fb108e63506973ccc5b07e4a9ad0ee07033e","tid":1882183,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T05:41:19.000Z","msg":"有「兒童奧斯卡」之稱的年度Nickelodeon Kids' Choice頒獎禮（NKCA）即將於3月22日加州舉行，漫威超級英雄賣座片《復仇者聯盟4：終局之戰》（Avengers：Endgame）橫掃11項最多提名，其中提名獎項包括最受歡迎電影與《阿拉丁》（Aladdin）及多部漫威超英片爭獎。而美國樂壇天后Taylor Swift亦獲5獎提名其中包括憑爛片《CATS》提名最受歡迎電影女演員與貝兒娜森（Brie Larson）及安祖蓮娜祖莉（Angelina Jolie）及Zendaya等女星爭獎！《CATS》最近才在金草莓獎獲8項最多提名。除了爭影后之外，Taylor亦提名最受歡迎女歌手與全球音樂巨星獎等。<br />\n此外，迪士尼賣座動畫《魔雪奇緣2》（Frozen II）、Henry Danger及Lil Nas X各獲4項提名。而韋史密夫（Will Smith）就憑《阿拉丁》爭最受歡迎電影男演員，他亦累積29次提名成為NKCA史上最多提名明星！"},{"pid":"b2ac05590ff83055d31ca3e2668283d274327791","tid":1882183,"uid":226155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T10:56:59.000Z","msg":"兒童奧斯卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06e5cd6b84f22bf63af7f1ebe7f773f2c36519f3","tid":1882183,"uid":17008,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T12:21:13.000Z","msg":"marvel fans會唔會難堪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ca6e3a494313fa50115340131e6c2d732165f91","tid":1882183,"uid":54431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T19:54:52.000Z","msg":"唔撚係掛<br />\n呢套垃圾都有得爭獎?"},{"pid":"6eb9b314bb443a9c1a05cb8cee91e87c6a3d5499","tid":1882183,"uid":3549,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"06e5cd6b84f22bf63af7f1ebe7f773f2c36519f3","tid":1882183,"uid":17008,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T12:21:13.000Z","msg":"marvel fans會唔會難堪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTi